Selected Answer: C
Global Reader can read everything that a Global Administrator can, but not update anything. So in the line of least privilege the answer should be C. Don't take my word for it, read the permissions on the link provided;
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/roles/permissions-reference#global-reader%20Global%20Reader%20cannot%20read%20Teams%20lifecycle,%20Analytics%20&%20reports,%20IP%20phone%20device%20management,%20and%20App%20catalog.%20For%20more%20information,%20see%20Use%20Microsoft%20Teams%20administrator%20roles%20to%20manage%20Teams.
